T02TD1707E:67b-1: shr'i ao di yan t'a re kra m'a bhi sa ma ya n'a ma /
T02TD1707E:67b-3: dpal au rgyan gyi sgrol ma'i mngon par rtogs pa'i rim pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD1707E:67b-4: 'phags ma sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1707E:67b-5: sdug bsngal srid pa'i mun pa ni //
T02TD1707E:67b-6: sel bar byed pa'i nyi 'od can //
T02TD1707E:67b-7: thugs kar snying rjes brlan pa la //
T02TD1707E:67b-8: rtag tu bdag ni phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1707E:67b-9: dang por re zhig rnal 'byor pa'am rnal 'byor mas /
T02TD1707E:67b-10: bsam gtan gyi khang pa yid dang mthun par 'jam pa'i stan la 'dug nas /
T02TD1707E:67b-11: rang gi snying gar aa las byung ba'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la t'am yig dmar po las 'od zer gyi tshogs 'phros pas ma lus pa'i nam mkha'i 'khor khyab par bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD1707E:67b-12: de nas 'od zer gyi zhal mthong bar bya ba'i ma lus pa'i bla ma dang /
T02TD1707E:67b-14: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams bltas te /
T02TD1707E:67b-15: de rnams la sems kyis mchod pa byas la /
T02TD1707E:67b-16: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba la sogs pa brjod de /
T02TD1707E:67b-17: de nas brtan pa dang g-yo ba'i 'gro ba rang bzhin gyis stong pa'i bdag nyid dang ldan par blta'o //
T02TD1707E:67b-19: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sv'a bh'a wa a'atma konyaham /
T02TD1707E:67b-20: de'i rjes su nam mkha' la padma dang nyi ma la gnas pa'i h'um yig las skyes pa'i khro bo'i rdo rjes bgegs bskrad do //
T02TD1707E:67b-21: rdo rje ra ba bsgom par gnas pa'i chos 'byung gi dbus su gzhal yas khang gi nang du /
T02TD1707E:67b-22: zla ba'i dbus su ham yig bltas te de nas ham yig las de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad spro bar bya ste /
T02TD1707E:67b-23: bdag nyid sgrol ma'i gzugs su bsgom par bya'o /
T02TD1707E:67b-24: sku mdog dmar mo zhal bzhi pa phyag brgyad pa gar byed pa /
T02TD1707E:67b-26: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD1707E:67b-27: stag gi pags pas smad g-yogs pa //
T02TD1707E:67b-28: rnal 'byor ma'i tshogs kyi dbus na gnas pa /
T02TD1707E:67b-31: de'i dang po'i zhal dmar po g-yas kyi gnag pa /
T02TD1707E:67b-33: steng du zhi ba ser po'i g-yas pa'i phyag rnams na /
T02TD1707E:68a-3: de nas tshogs padma lha mo brgyad /
T02TD1707E:68a-4: su ra ti shva ri dang /
T02TD1707E:68a-7: su ra ta ma li ni /
T02TD1707E:68a-9: su ra ta ka mi ni /
T02TD1707E:68a-20: ji ltar g-yas kyis da ma ru dang ka p'a la 'dzin pa /
T02TD1707E:68a-21: g-yon pa rnams kyis dril bu dang kha tv'am ga 'dzin pa /
T02TD1707E:68a-24: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD1707E:68a-25: de'i phyi rol du 'khor lo rtsibs bcu gnyis pa la shi khi bhi ma /
T02TD1707E:68a-36: narta ki / de dag thams cad g-yon phyed dmar pa /
T02TD1707E:68a-38: g-yas na 'khor lo dang rdo rje 'dzin pa /
T02TD1707E:68a-42: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD1707E:68a-45: g-yon bskum g-yas brkyang gi gar gyis g-yas pa /
T02TD1707E:68a-48: gzhan yang de'i phyi rol du sgo bzhi ma /
T02TD1707E:68a-52: ma tam g'i / g-yas na gri gug dang thod pa 'dzin pa /
T02TD1707E:68a-56: sprul gyi rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
T02TD1707E:68a-57: nyi ma'i gdan la g-yon bskum g-yas brkyang bas bdud bzhi'i steng du g-yon du bskor ba /
T02TD1707E:68a-58: kha dog sna tshogs bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD1707E:68a-59: de nas gnas kyi cho ga bya ste /
T02TD1707E:68a-74: thugs ka / lte ba'i 'og / gsang gnas /
T02TD1707E:68a-79: rkang pa'i 'og / rkang pa'i mthe bong /
T02TD1707E:68a-80: pus mo gnyis la rim pa ji lta bar /
T02TD1707E:68b-1: k'a ao tri ko / ka la k'a hi /
T02TD1707E:68b-20: ka lim ga / lam p'a kam /'du ba gnyis so //
T02TD1707E:68b-29: nye ba'i ma la ya gnyis so /
T02TD1707E:68b-33: ma ru di sham / ku lu t'a /
T02TD1707E:68b-34: nye ba'i dur khrod gnyis so //
T02TD1707E:68b-39: byin pa la rim pa bzhin du /
T02TD1707E:68b-40: bhr'um bhr'um aa hrim kham zhes bya ba ni go cha'o //
T02TD1707E:68b-41: de rdo rje padma 'khor lo'i dbus su h'um a'a: aom /
T02TD1707E:68b-43: ye shes can gyis bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD1707E:68b-44: de nas dbang bskur bar bya'o //
T02TD1707E:68b-45: lha mo'i dbu la de bzhin gshegs pa lnga /
T02TD1707E:68b-46: su ra ti shva ri la sogs pa la /
T02TD1707E:68b-47: dbu la rin chen 'byung ldan no //
T02TD1707E:68b-48: shi khi la sogs pa rnams la dbu la rnam par snang mdzad /
T02TD1707E:68b-49: kam pu tsi la sogs pa rnams la dbu la mi bskyod pa'o //
T02TD1707E:68b-50: de nas aargham sbyin par bya'o //
T02TD1707E:68b-51: de nas bdud rtsi myang bar bya'o //
T02TD1707E:68b-52: de la yam ram las dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi steng du padma'i snod bdud rtsi lngas bkang nas sha / go ha aa ma aom a'a: h'um des sbyin gyis brlab po //
T02TD1707E:68b-53: de nas sngags bzlas pa ni /
T02TD1707E:68b-54: yi ge bcu phat mthar sbyang sv'a h'a mthar spangs pa'o //
T02TD1707E:68b-55: lha mo la bzlas pa byas pa thams cad la aom sngar ming gi yi ge mthar h'um phat sngags bzlas so //
T02TD1707E:68b-56: dza: h'um bam ho: dang ldan pa sgo'i lha mo rnams la'o //
T02TD1707E:68b-57: bsgom pa las langs nas lha mo'i gzugs su 'dzin par bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD1707E:68b-58: ji ltar nus pas mchod pa'o //
T02TD1707E:68b-61: aom aa k'a ro mu kham sarba dharm'a n'am a'adya nutpanna tv'ata aom a'a: h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1707E:68b-62: zhes bya ba rtag tu byas na grub pa thob po //
T02TD1707E:69a-0: de la the tshom ma byed cig / bcom ldan 'das ma au @69a * //
T02TD1707E:69a-1: rgyan gyi sgrol ma'i mngon par rtogs pa'i rim pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1707E:69a-3: // / thugs rje chen pos dbang lan gsum bskur ba'i grub thob wi ni ta bha dra'i slob ma pandi ta sam gha shr'i bha dra dang /
T02TD1707E:69a-4: bod kyi lo ts'a ba 'jam dpal sgeg ba'i rdo rjes bsgyur ba'o /
